<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Reference copy of the BehaviorSpace experiment embedded in
  breeding_storm_predation2.nlogox (NetLogo 7 format).

  NetLogo 7 changes vs. the classic format:
    - timeLimit is an attribute on <experiment>, not a child element
    - sequentialRunOrder is a required attribute on <experiment>
    - metrics are wrapped in a <metrics> block
    - constants/variables are wrapped in a <constants> block
-->
